{"tid":616942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇圖]｛借錢緊唔還，做人千祈唔好心軟｝","createTime":"2018-04-04T15:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T13:54:34.000Z","uid":31104,"like":15,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"50cae1654ec5641d969c765a81951e7cc6f5d934","tid":616942,"uid":31104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:02:43.000Z","msg":"話說呢條友,半年前借咗我朋友總共8000$<br />\n一直都話遲啲先還 到最後失埋蹤<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/224221_3093ae745a313a71db6789bf7cbb84b8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F224221_3093ae745a313a71db6789bf7cbb84b8.png&h=9a7be8cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇下條柒頭d相先<br />\n姓名：彭崇成 國籍：蝗 年齡：23-25<br />\n父母關係：離婚 有一個啊哥<br />\n住址：東涌逸東村美逸樓<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/223701_a8b1e3782797bbdd7e3e504715c4a9b7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F223701_a8b1e3782797bbdd7e3e504715c4a9b7.png&h=08447b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/223703_8e4784c18c78da7fd90d9aa09d9a4a4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F223703_8e4784c18c78da7fd90d9aa09d9a4a4c.png&h=b527ee17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我唔明點解呢d人 可以咁恐怖<br />\n問你借錢一個樣 借完之後就失蹤<br />\n- - - - - - - - - - -<br />\n當初話佢老豆喺大陸要錢做手術<br />\n朋友好心借左比佢<br />\n<br />\n點知原來佢攞啲錢黎吸毒同埋玩食雞<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/225119_36d6eadac467aae211f5aa7bd5ee91dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F225119_36d6eadac467aae211f5aa7bd5ee91dd.png&h=67b1ec05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/225120_a0c972e3e8b2dd1c275f0f500673af11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F225120_a0c972e3e8b2dd1c275f0f500673af11.png&h=545d1d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人哋好心借錢俾你俾你周轉 點知你就攞嚟吸毒<br />\n<br />\n子華神冇講錯 ：[借錢比朋友周轉有分自轉及公轉，借比佢時就叫自轉(1日要收到數)，但到還錢時就係公轉（好多年）]<br />\n<br />\n同埋真係唔明乜撚嘅係食雞毒<br />\n點解呢條垃圾可以三個月唔返工係屋企係咁玩食雞<br />\n如果你老豆真係有事 咁真係抵佢死<br />\n生左你呢啲咁嘅廢柴出嚟<br />\n<br />\n奉勸咁多位真係唔好亂咁借錢俾人<br />\n如果唔係喊都無謂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/230114_868262276a734cfd00ef71b6613975a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F230114_868262276a734cfd00ef71b6613975a1.png&h=70c8cbb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢啲新移民 大陸仔真係恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262b37460a5bc340d00f43da91af811a5c7969cd","tid":616942,"uid":96,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:05:55.000Z","msg":"新移民都借 唔抵可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745ff911bdfdf25aa09181ff87d09cc6569277d6","tid":616942,"uid":68081,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:07:55.000Z","msg":"大陸仔都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed040709e6b213975f0995d4dcee9c77d2d6f69","tid":616942,"uid":31104,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"點解我要開呢個post呢<br />\n係因為聽朋友講 佢呢排又出去蒲<br />\n香港大陸兩邊玩<br />\n有錢都唔撚還正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/230635_d818fc632c56d314aec4ea3629ef6c5d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F230635_d818fc632c56d314aec4ea3629ef6c5d.png&h=3d936814&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/230642_1b46bcdba2f78917eed07b125bebfa03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F230642_1b46bcdba2f78917eed07b125bebfa03.png&h=daaa3c50&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/230646_13068ea7678324d2c0866e222fc83cf2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F230646_13068ea7678324d2c0866e222fc83cf2.png&h=5d5b3d1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/230651_409c5073d38345992d0cecb5e340fed8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F230651_409c5073d38345992d0cecb5e340fed8.png&h=8212bf44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/230708_18e1e2ca44aaaefdcc5b41a21925871b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F230708_18e1e2ca44aaaefdcc5b41a21925871b.png&h=538e0f26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爭人錢嗰啲撚樣好快啲還錢<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/230710_dfe8c6d1a59746463cd55454aaecdcd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F230710_dfe8c6d1a59746463cd55454aaecdcd5.png&h=741bc162&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2b5ba80846cd87e7d0c9ff8432caa5d7c92c4e3","tid":616942,"uid":31104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"262b37460a5bc340d00f43da91af811a5c7969cd","tid":616942,"uid":96,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:05:55.000Z","msg":"新移民都借 唔抵可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:08:49.000Z","msg":"因為一啲關係佢地識咗兩三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced243c5fa14fb0f08bce77f34015cd99023c3d2","tid":616942,"uid":31104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"745ff911bdfdf25aa09181ff87d09cc6569277d6","tid":616942,"uid":68081,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:07:55.000Z","msg":"大陸仔都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"蝗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c73dcdb0270dce38c1c59169192f66866fe69c","tid":616942,"uid":137997,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:10:55.000Z","msg":"啲錢係我用實力借返來 點解要還 屌你老母"},{"pid":"5cec3ac1d3cd59caf77b655fa1c7a25e4d369bf6","tid":616942,"uid":137997,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲錢係我用實力借返來 點解要還 屌你老母.jpg</blockquote>"},{"pid":"97c0200f30de1ff11622990394e935068b7b3c29","tid":616942,"uid":31104,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:12:39.000Z","msg":"總之同身邊嘅朋友講下<br />\n見到佢就避開啦<br />\n因為條友兩年前喺油麻地診所打過性病針<br />\n唔記得咩性病 嗰陣時佢好似俾人通緝緊<br />\n然後因為係屎窟打咗針<br />\n咁岩撞正差佬 俾人查身分證<br />\n然後佢走咗去果欄 匿埋<br />\n但係最後佢屎窟太痛走唔郁訓咗喺度<br />\n比差佬帶返差館<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真人真事<br />\n我另外一個朋友當時係現場見到"},{"pid":"06cef6cdaae382e813274d5433bcedcd36d3a83b","tid":616942,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:12:52.000Z","msg":"買個教訓<br />\n呢世都唔好再借錢畀人喇"},{"pid":"013b7455560c2b03e83559b8987ec3a1fdd2d7d1","tid":616942,"uid":163797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:13:15.000Z","msg":"借錢唔還正仆街"},{"pid":"f7740c91a5fa98403b8053d74fc8a3e860ad725e","tid":616942,"uid":31104,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"5cec3ac1d3cd59caf77b655fa1c7a25e4d369bf6","tid":616942,"uid":137997,"like":8,"dislike":0